    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "When we restart, we need both finalized block and finalized state and we start from the latest finalized state (aka `lastKnownState`). I'd order the `ArchiveBlocks` then `ArchiveState` in `TasksService` so that when we restart we're sure to get the finalized block from `ArchiveBlock` database.\r\n\r\n> it shouldn't really matter as we will just resync from last stored finalized block?\r\n\r\nI think we resync from the finalized block respective to the last stored finalized state",
